import React from 'react'; import { conenct, connect } from 'react-redux'; import { createStructuredSelector } from 'reselect'; import {selectCartItems, selectCartTotal} from '../../redux/cart/cart.selectors' import './checkout.styles.scss'; const CheckoutPage = ({cartItems, total}) => (
Product
Description
Quantity
Price
Remove
{ cartItems.map(cartItem => cartItem.name ) }
TOTAL: ${total}
) const mapStateToProps = createStructuredSelector({ cartItems: selectCartItems, total: selectCartTotal }) export default connect(mapStateToProps)(CheckoutPage);
